02:06.000Z","msg":"白晶晶鐘意孫悟空<br />\n至尊寶鐘意白晶晶<br />\n紫霞鐘意至尊寶<br />\n孫悟空鐘意紫霞<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9341247962c4a18319539952ceeabf3e2b4daff2","tid":791394,"uid":165202,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"白晶晶愛的是孫悟空，愛白晶晶的是至尊寶;<br />\n紫霞愛的是至尊寶，愛紫霞的是孫悟空。<br />\n你以為是同一個人，其實已經相隔500年。"},{"pid":"e7e6fe66deb3eccfc7e12e04bc55cf27e1dbe372","tid":791394,"uid":182314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"晶晶鐘意孫悟空，紫霞鐘意至尊寶"},{"pid":"468f996a1c8a021f3cee4cdfd6c7fbd12dfa7f28","tid":791394,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:05:42.000Z","msg":"個結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次睇完都sad 但就因為咁先刻骨銘心"},{"pid":"192b7a95ee674b63e077cc7e65fb1cfcb556f958","tid":791394,"uid":124746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97afe2ebcc7ab308bcf6467860d87d332c2afff6","tid":791394,"uid":91096,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"最慘應該係孫悟空  以為經歷左段真摯、刻骨銘心既感情<br />\n結果最後只係一場空  只係為左迫佢死心  斷七情六慾去取經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"真係好慘"},{"pid":"82e2ec8a9ac3f583ab0a0d20991e4fe20b83274a","tid":791394,"uid":146982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d00c17a08e49a8cbcee2fa939424a4842f1bc93","tid":791394,"uid":15205,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"至尊寶愛白晶晶<br />\n白晶晶愛孫悟空<br />\n孫悟空愛紫霞<br />\n紫霞愛至尊寶/孫悟空"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45de7d9aac43b6f31304ff03ab310a52237a10ff","tid":791394,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"有幾幕的確係好笑拍得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋呢套戲入邊既朱因係全盛時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係宏觀成套戲故事內容同銜接簡直係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a7929584b091337a3edd638b013535fdda2097","tid":791394,"uid":124746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45de7d9aac43b6f31304ff03ab310a52237a10ff","tid":791394,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"有幾幕的確係好笑拍得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋呢套戲入邊既朱因係全盛時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係宏觀成套戲故事內容同銜接簡直係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"朱因真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d633928dc5687c3448d54b0a62449d4005ad08b1","tid":791394,"uid":149765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"至尊寶鐘意白晶晶<br />\n白晶晶鐘意孫悟空<br />\n孫悟空鐘意紫霞<br />\n紫霞鐘意至尊寶<br />\nSad"},{"pid":"ba96c1e06283bb69b92c4362c15717dd1949a48d","tid":791394,"uid":15644,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"344bfd10d0403c91703a2d22d5a5821cb75b1403","tid":791394,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"單睇第二集, 紫霞同孫悟空果段係幾可歌可泣<br />\n但成套咁睇, 晶晶同悟空其實仲可惜, 經歷仲多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一集咁辛苦先同到晶晶一齊, 由搵到佢, 再想殺佢, 到救佢, 到一齊傾心事, 準備扑野, 誤會, 自殺, 經歷生死, 終於認清真心愛對方, <br />\n最終為左晶晶時空超越左500年前<br />\n<br />\n第二集同紫霞其實無咩經歷, 一開始孫悟空只係搵晶晶, 係無意中拔左佢劍, 就話要嫁佢。之後假結婚講句假既世界對白, 當時孫悟空都唔係認真。<br />\n之後搵返晶晶, 但就無啦啦講返孫悟空最愛係紫霞..然後晶晶就黯然消失左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後悟空先專心一意想救返紫霞<br />\n<br />\n即係500年後, 晶晶仲苦等緊孫悟空(至尊寶), <br />\n但孫悟空愛上左一個經歷較少既紫霞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"其實晶晶無等佢500年<br />\n因為番左去500年前未變孫悟空既至尊寶係轉世為人再番去500年前 <br />\n係平衡時空黎 <br />\n<br />\n以前果d 女全部都係500年前既佢溝<br />\n可能晶晶鍾意既只係500年前既佢<br />\n唔係轉世為人之後既佢"},{"pid":"3f15bcb2264443144f31e485c42f07e8f3732d82","tid":791394,"uid":45817,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"成套戲都係講命運<br />\n命中注定至尊寶拔到把劍<br />\n攪一大輪就為左穿越500年遇到紫霞<br />\n最尾呼應返在命運面前，強如齊天大聖都似隻狗一樣<br />\n無能為力"},{"pid":"6fc73e0ff3544b68436c268a6da8988fa9596629","tid":791394,"uid":111372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"白晶晶係自己苦心追求，紫霞係掉轉被女追，紫霞先用劍個吹撚漲理由，跟著到牛魔王婚禮既連命都唔要感動左佢，就係咁。"},{"pid":"a23ccf4be7825a80882b1ad13f3a69e568b9d51a","tid":791394,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"首歌真係好正"},{"pid":"84c286f1bee2cb29d9ea9cef8e1beb8b8af916a2","tid":791394,"uid":194380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"呢套真係拍得好撚有深度但又不失商業既角度。<br />\n記得好細個係去阿麻到拜年 啲大人係到打牌 而我老豆就帶我入場睇呢套戲，仲記得睇完覺得好唔夠喉，原來仲有下集就好失落因為要等多一年先有得睇。"},{"pid":"46043d29eeec73b5eb72c2365c93c45b4d1d8b01","tid":791394,"uid":194380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a23ccf4be7825a80882b1ad13f3a69e568b9d51a","tid":791394,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"首歌真係好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"相親竟不可接近"},{"pid":"3a370028b6859fbe4b4d7200cfe517e33ca56e7c","tid":791394,"uid":12159,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"18f61dd70113234f00f2cf7229dc17069d47d8b5","tid":791394,"uid":152799,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"&quot;如果個天要我鐘意豬八戒 我都無辦法架&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"嘔嘔下就慣"},{"pid":"159d47de9bcc907825548388d504bce1e3653f8c","tid":791394,"uid":82593,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d9cb05c879d3bd3b2fc7ffaec77c3ba5a9473a56","tid":791394,"uid":58022,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,