assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"2a350d1513b803a3045a42369711568812858803","tid":791394,"uid":2207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"西遊記第一次睇係笑到喊<br />\n大少少再睇 都係喊<br />\n不過喊係因為有經歷 終於睇得明以前唔明既野<br />\n<br />\n呢套一定係周星馳top 3"},{"pid":"8ef3ef26dd2fc865d3bcfd6aa0ee851560e04419","tid":791394,"uid":199881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"苦海 翻起愛恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e9af3fc7d400d6383104a784ee0a844132a9bb","tid":791394,"uid":193665,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qRP4hZDu09w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqRP4hZDu09w&d=wCS1pVCWk9FORZ9yatMrf8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=dbc624b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qRP4hZDu09w</a>"},{"pid":"c268ef0616650cbb9779470ed5e5b90424fce31f","tid":791394,"uid":90479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ff3937a7510117d69ea9a67ca2a169557af409c","tid":791394,"uid":294,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"cc53ef34349ad9bad401bfb0afed183a2db951d5","tid":791394,"uid":73443,"like":127,"dislike":6,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:20:07.000Z","msg":"應該係咁睇<br />\n晶晶就好比你拍左拖好多年<br />\n感情好好<br />\n就黎結婚既女朋友<br />\n<br />\n紫霞就係工司新請既見習<br />\n好激烈好青春感染力強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:23:37.000Z","msg":"但晶晶同孫悟空都未正式一齊, 只係岩岩經歷生死, 認清對方, 就要分開<br />\n第二集搵返晶晶結婚, 然後晶晶不遲而別果度, 果種憂傷肋住肋住好撚慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得第二集有d 專登淡化左晶晶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"其實係其中一樣套戲想帶出ge野<br />\n愛情唔係睇經歷幾多野 時間 黎定<br />\n係要睇兩個人心中最愛係邊個"},{"pid":"41b9d1488d5d4ce6e2dd733b4144f47e9677d9dd","tid":791394,"uid":180383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"至尊寶鍾意白晶晶<br />\n白晶晶鍾意孫悟空<br />\n孫悟空鍾意紫霞<br />\n紫霞鍾意至尊寶<br />\n天意弄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ed019a4d8d939699eef167d4f770bbb6f2402b","tid":791394,"uid":170375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"可能正因為係戲先感到可惜<br />\n好多時 人同至尊寶一樣 為一樣野執著 迷戀<br />\n但永遠往往到後期，對命運感到無力 <br />\n做算你係齊天大聖都改變唔到任何野<br />\n諗下 如果唔變大聖 紫霞自殺<br />\n但你變左大聖都係被人打死<br />\n比你有通天之能 但區區一位女子命運都不能改變<br />\n因此好多人細時愛神鵰 童話般劇情<br />\n長大後 天龍八部 反而更吸引 <br />\n因此要好似最後孫悟空放下一切離開 踏上悟道之旅<br />\n比起成為齊天大聖，我情願做凡人 體驗無常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2539b124a1b3bb2373d2af0237a1b0c43c839d70","tid":791394,"uid":158499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e3dfc469bee0a632e1c4eeb4ffa474c0af8b4c1","tid":791394,"uid":48623,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bfee323bf3bc4ea0e152404614bce70a9b74998d","tid":791394,"uid":1790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"97afe2ebcc7ab308bcf6467860d87d332c2afff6","tid":791394,"uid":91096,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"最慘應該係孫悟空  以為經歷左段真摯、刻骨銘心既感情<br />\n結果最後只係一場空  只係為左迫佢死心  斷七情六慾去取經"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:21:32.000Z","msg":"個故事就係想你明放下執著同人世間所有嘅事物都係空"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"調轉來睇，叫佢取西經感化世人既神佛某程度上都係執著。攪咁多野為左令佢放下執著，但偏偏佢地就執著於感化世人取西經。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"大乘佛教最中心嘅思想係普度眾生，一切皆空只係叫你放下對世事嘅執著..<br />\n取西經正正就係為左普度眾生"},{"pid":"6f1e10493e8323430b94a720535d4567b1cbadeb","tid":791394,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f15bcb2264443144f31e485c42f07e8f3732d82","tid":791394,"uid":45817,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"成套戲都係講命運<br />\n命中注定至尊寶拔到把劍<br />\n攪一大輪就為左穿越500年遇到紫霞<br />\n最尾呼應返在命運面前，強如齊天大聖都似隻狗一樣<br />\n無能為力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"終極歸納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2011ee3e3e3bc556c170a7e72899842a67bb243","tid":791394,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"晶晶鐘意孫悟空<br />\n至尊寶只係一個代替品"},{"pid":"89c24f5cfcd9fe35d939d9ea5f666565a7d19be1","tid":791394,"uid":5597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"白晶晶對至尊寶關係唔係單純既愛，有d 係替代左之前一段遺憾咁，好似人到左某年紀，你揀另一半唔再係純愛出發...<br />\n相反紫霞代表左好單純既愛，鐘意一個人，可能只係一d 好on9既原因/緣。<br />\n而周星馳就好比你內心，問心如果有得揀你會點揀？<br />\n然後現實係你無得揀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd7cd969c71ed18a111673a4d59f2a0bd3d5685","tid":791394,"uid":140167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"點解至尊寶唔係孫悟空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae59c0434676c2820f507875fdd02a2d3a91396","tid":791394,"uid":39734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"應該咁講 你經歷多啲就明<br />\n多回憶=/=最愛"},{"pid":"4e3e1712bd0624a531463c354b38c5589648b3a1","tid":791394,"uid":192537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bc414f524bf6971e64159c84a990e95bb1c55b9","tid":791394,"uid":89981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"係上天安排 大哂"},{"pid":"b769530a4fbef0599c27826048fca2700cc76ec0","tid":791394,"uid":192537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:16:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d98f1183bf998f5333476542b7e3e0e4e2277c98","tid":791394,"uid":89981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"為左一個女人回到500年前， 但又即刻愛上另一個女人 ， 將來可能有另一個紫霞 晶晶 ， 所以都係去取西經啦"},{"pid":"0e72beedc12f9fe4c203d0b697b01ee5d68c87b9","tid":791394,"uid":190253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"細個睇唔明個種感覺